                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Choice of styles</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Durable construction</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Weather resistant</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>USPS compliant</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Get Quote
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Premium Package -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-600 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Premium Package</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">$495</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">High-end mailbox for maximum curb appeal</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Everything in Standard</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Premium mailbox</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Decorative post options</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Custom finishes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Large capacity</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Enhanced durability</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Get Quote
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Multi-Mailbox -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-600 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Multi-Mailbox</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">Custom</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">For shared driveways and duplexes</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>2-3 mailbox systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Heavy-duty post</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Reinforced foundation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Uniform appearance</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>HOA compliant options</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Professional installation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Get Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Repair Pricing -->
  <section id="repair" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Repair Services</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Affordable repairs to extend the life of your mailbox
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Minor Repair</h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">$95</div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li>• Door hinge repair</li>
            <li>• Flag replacement</li>
            <li>• Hardware tightening</li>
            <li>• Minor adjustments</li>
            <li>• Quick fixes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Post Stabilization</h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">$165</div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li>• Straighten leaning post</li>
            <li>• Reinforce foundation</li>
            <li>• Additional concrete</li>
            <li>• Post bracing</li>
            <li>• Stability restoration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Emergency Service</h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">+$85</div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li>• Same-day service</li>
            <li>• Rapid response</li>
            <li>• After-hours available</li>
            <li>• Storm damage</li>
            <li>• Vehicle damage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Services Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Additional Services</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Enhance your curb appeal with these add-on services
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Service</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Price Range</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-900">House Number Installation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">$75 - $125</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-900">Mailbox Painting/Refinishing</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">$75 - $150</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-900">Post Light Installation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">$100 - $200</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-900">Decorative Post Cap</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">$15 - $50</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-900">Custom Color Matching</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">$50 - $100</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Pricing FAQs</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer free quotes?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes! We provide free, no-obligation quotes for all services. Contact us with photos and details, and we'll provide an accurate estimate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We accept cash, checks, credit cards, and digital payments for your convenience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is there a travel fee?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We serve Calvert, St. Mary's, and Charles Counties with no travel fee for most locations. Distant areas may have a modest travel charge of $25-$50.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you require a deposit?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">For standard installations, payment is due upon completion. Custom orders or premium installations may require a 25-50% deposit.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are there any hidden fees?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No hidden fees! Our quotes include all labor, materials, and cleanup. The only additional charges would be for services you specifically request.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-blue-600 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-blue-100">
        Contact us today for a free, no-obligation quote
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
        Request Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
